posts.message:
Kite is a heads up display (HUD) for programmers that surfaces proven engineering knowledge in a live internet­ connected environment helping developers write better code, faster.
Kite is the first tool to offer a connected way to program; it is integrated with text editors and it uses type inference to reveal examples as programmers type without having to leave the screen for a web browser.
posts.caption: kite.com
posts.description: The artificial pair programmer that shows you examples, documentation, and even fixes simple errors for you.
